39 (13) Carbaryl, not to exceed 500 parts per billion for ingestion or 500 parts per
40 billion for inhalation.
41 (14) Carbofuran, not to exceed 100 parts per billion for ingestion or inhalation.
42 (15) Chlorantraniliprole, not to exceed 3,000 parts per billion for ingestion or 1,000
